  <title>5.4.1 Disposal of Waste Oil, Waste Fluids and Waste Materials</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>#MECHOK</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">废油，废液和费材料的处理</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:8px; line-height:1.18;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">需要根据贵国法律，法规和条例处理诸如切削液，润滑脂，液压油，润滑油，碎屑或石墨灰等机床操作排泄的废物。</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.18;"><text style="font-size:11pt;">此外，还要适当分选可回收材料。</text></para>
  </body>
</topic>
